From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Soultaco83 <soulnacho@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Jun 2026 22:00:00 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Make SyncPlay timing parameters configurable via
 server configuration

SyncPlay's DefaultPing (500ms), MaxPlaybackOffset (500ms), and other
timing parameters are hardcoded in Group.cs. These values are tuned for
LAN/low-latency connections and cause constant re-syncing, pauses, and
buffering issues with high-latency connections (e.g., trans-pacific
USA->Australia with ~250ms RTT + jitter).

This patch:
- Adds SyncPlayOptions configuration class with default values matching
  the original hardcoded values (backward compatible).
- Adds SyncPlayOptions property to ServerConfiguration so it's stored
  in system.xml and editable via the dashboard.
- Inject IServerConfigurationManager into SyncPlayManager and pass
  options to Group constructor.
- Group reads DefaultPing, MaxPlaybackOffset, TimeSyncOffset, and
  BufferingTimeoutMs from the options instead of hardcoded values.

To tune for high-latency connections, edit system.xml:
  <SyncPlayOptions>
    <DefaultPing>1000</DefaultPing>
    <MaxPlaybackOffset>2000</MaxPlaybackOffset>
    <TimeSyncOffset>2000</TimeSyncOffset>
    <BufferingTimeoutMs>30000</BufferingTimeoutMs>
  </SyncPlayOptions>

diff --git a/Emby.Server.Implementations/SyncPlay/Group.cs b/Emby.Server.Implementations/SyncPlay/Group.cs
index f2ccaba82c..6e0ff590de 100644
--- a/Emby.Server.Implementations/SyncPlay/Group.cs
+++ b/Emby.Server.Implementations/SyncPlay/Group.cs
@@ -69,11 +69,13 @@ namespace Emby.Server.Implementations.SyncPlay
         /// <param name="userManager">The user manager.</param>
         /// <param name="sessionManager">The session manager.</param>
         /// <param name="libraryManager">The library manager.</param>
+        /// <param name="syncPlayOptions">The SyncPlay timing options.</param>
         public Group(
             ILoggerFactory loggerFactory,
             IUserManager userManager,
             ISessionManager sessionManager,
-            ILibraryManager libraryManager)
+            ILibraryManager libraryManager,
+            MediaBrowser.Model.Configuration.SyncPlayOptions syncPlayOptions)
         {
             _loggerFactory = loggerFactory;
             _userManager = userManager;
@@ -81,6 +83,11 @@ namespace Emby.Server.Implementations.SyncPlay
             _libraryManager = libraryManager;
             _logger = loggerFactory.CreateLogger<Group>();

+            DefaultPing = syncPlayOptions.DefaultPing;
+            MaxPlaybackOffset = syncPlayOptions.MaxPlaybackOffset;
+            TimeSyncOffset = syncPlayOptions.TimeSyncOffset;
+            BufferingTimeoutMs = syncPlayOptions.BufferingTimeoutMs;
+
             _state = new IdleGroupState(loggerFactory);
         }

